---
import '~/styles/capabilities.css';

---

<section class="section">
  <h2>Core Capabilities</h2>
  <div class="capabilities-grid">
    <div class="capability-card">
      <div class="capability-icon">🎓</div>
      <h3>Training & Education</h3>
      <p>
        Empowering teams through tailored training sessions and workshops
        covering Data Science, Machine Learning, Generative AI, and DevSecOps.
        My approach bridges theory and practical application, equipping your
        team with actionable skills for immediate impact.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="capability-card">
      <div class="capability-icon">🎯</div>
      <h3>Data & AI Strategy Consulting</h3>
      <p>
        Guiding strategic initiatives with deep expertise in data engineering,
        AI-driven analytics, cloud-native infrastructures, and governance
        frameworks to unlock sustained value from your data assets and ensure
        competitive advantage.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="capability-card">
      <div class="capability-icon">🚀</div>
      <h3>AI Transformation</h3>
      <p>
        Leading your organization into the next generation of Digital
        Transformation by integrating cutting-edge AI capabilities directly into
        your operational and decision-making processes for maximum efficiency
        and innovation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="capability-card">
      <div class="capability-icon">⚙️</div>
      <h3>Automation & Operational Excellence</h3>
      <p>
        Implementing xOps methodologies and homegrown frameworks underpinned by
        robust Infrastructure-as-Code solutions like Pulumi, streamlining
        operations, ensuring security, and driving significant efficiency gains.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="capability-card">
      <div class="capability-icon">🛠️</div>
      <h3>Product Development & Platform Engineering</h3>
      <p>
        Innovating with custom-built on-premises Generative AI solutions (AI
        Agent in a Box), SaaS product engineering, and scalable platform
        architectures designed specifically to your organizational needs and
        strategic vision.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="capability-card">
      <div class="capability-icon">🏛️</div>
      <h3>DoD & Government Expertise</h3>
      <p>
        Specialized experience working with Department of Defense clients and
        government agencies, ensuring compliance with security requirements
        while delivering innovative AI solutions that meet mission-critical
        objectives.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
